Name: azure_aclmatchedpackets_average;azure_aclmatchedpackets_count;azure_aclmatchedpackets_maximum;azure_aclmatchedpackets_minimum;azure_aclmatchedpackets_total
Description: Count of the number of packets matching the current ACL entry.

Name: azure_bgppeerstatus_average;azure_bgppeerstatus_count;azure_bgppeerstatus_maximum;azure_bgppeerstatus_minimum;azure_bgppeerstatus_total
Description: Operational state of the BGP peer. State is represented in numerical form. Idle : 1, Connect : 2, Active : 3, Opensent : 4, Openconfirm : 5, Established : 6

Name: azure_componentoperstatus_average;azure_componentoperstatus_count;azure_componentoperstatus_maximum;azure_componentoperstatus_minimum;azure_componentoperstatus_total
Description: The current operational status of the component.

Name: azure_cpuutilizationmax_average;azure_cpuutilizationmax_count;azure_cpuutilizationmax_maximum;azure_cpuutilizationmax_minimum;azure_cpuutilizationmax_total
Description: Max cpu utilization. The maximum value of the percentage measure of the statistic over the time interval.

Name: azure_cpuutilizationmin_average;azure_cpuutilizationmin_count;azure_cpuutilizationmin_maximum;azure_cpuutilizationmin_minimum;azure_cpuutilizationmin_total
Description: Min cpu utilization. The minimum value of the percentage measure of the statistic over the time interval.

Name: azure_fanspeed_average;azure_fanspeed_count;azure_fanspeed_maximum;azure_fanspeed_minimum;azure_fanspeed_total
Description: Current fan speed.

Name: azure_ifethincrcerrors_average;azure_ifethincrcerrors_count;azure_ifethincrcerrors_maximum;azure_ifethincrcerrors_minimum;azure_ifethincrcerrors_total
Description: The total number of frames received that had a length (excluding framing bits, but including FCS octets) of between 64 and 1518 octets, inclusive, but had either a bad Frame Check Sequence (FCS) with an integral number of octets (FCS Error) or a bad FCS with a non-integral number of octets (Alignment Error)

Name: azure_ifethinfragmentframes_average;azure_ifethinfragmentframes_count;azure_ifethinfragmentframes_maximum;azure_ifethinfragmentframes_minimum;azure_ifethinfragmentframes_total
Description: The total number of frames received that were less than 64 octets in length (excluding framing bits but including FCS octets) and had either a bad Frame Check Sequence (FCS) with an integral number of octets (FCS Error) or a bad FCS with a non-integral number of octets (Alignment Error).

Name: azure_ifethinjabberframes_average;azure_ifethinjabberframes_count;azure_ifethinjabberframes_maximum;azure_ifethinjabberframes_minimum;azure_ifethinjabberframes_total
Description: Number of jabber frames received on the interface. Jabber frames are typically defined as oversize frames which also have a bad CRC.

Name: azure_ifethinmaccontrolframes_average;azure_ifethinmaccontrolframes_count;azure_ifethinmaccontrolframes_maximum;azure_ifethinmaccontrolframes_minimum;azure_ifethinmaccontrolframes_total
Description: MAC layer control frames received on the interface

Name: azure_ifethinmacpauseframes_average;azure_ifethinmacpauseframes_count;azure_ifethinmacpauseframes_maximum;azure_ifethinmacpauseframes_minimum;azure_ifethinmacpauseframes_total
Description: MAC layer PAUSE frames received on the interface

Name: azure_ifethinmaxsizeexceeded_average;azure_ifethinmaxsizeexceeded_count;azure_ifethinmaxsizeexceeded_maximum;azure_ifethinmaxsizeexceeded_minimum;azure_ifethinmaxsizeexceeded_total
Description: The total number frames received that are well-formed dropped due to exceeding the maximum frame size on the interface.

Name: azure_ifethinoversizeframes_average;azure_ifethinoversizeframes_count;azure_ifethinoversizeframes_maximum;azure_ifethinoversizeframes_minimum;azure_ifethinoversizeframes_total
Description: The total number of frames received that were longer than 1518 octets (excluding framing bits, but including FCS octets) and were otherwise well formed.

Name: azure_ifethoutmaccontrolframes_average;azure_ifethoutmaccontrolframes_count;azure_ifethoutmaccontrolframes_maximum;azure_ifethoutmaccontrolframes_minimum;azure_ifethoutmaccontrolframes_total
Description: MAC layer control frames sent on the interface.

Name: azure_ifethoutmacpauseframes_average;azure_ifethoutmacpauseframes_count;azure_ifethoutmacpauseframes_maximum;azure_ifethoutmacpauseframes_minimum;azure_ifethoutmacpauseframes_total
Description: MAC layer PAUSE frames sent on the interface.

Name: azure_ifinbroadcastpkts_average;azure_ifinbroadcastpkts_count;azure_ifinbroadcastpkts_maximum;azure_ifinbroadcastpkts_minimum;azure_ifinbroadcastpkts_total
Description: The number of packets, delivered by this sub-layer to a higher (sub-)layer, that were addressed to a broadcast address at this sub-layer.

Name: azure_ifindiscards_average;azure_ifindiscards_count;azure_ifindiscards_maximum;azure_ifindiscards_minimum;azure_ifindiscards_total
Description: The number of inbound packets that were chosen to be discarded even though no errors had been detected to prevent their being deliverable to a higher-layer protocol.

Name: azure_ifinerrors_average;azure_ifinerrors_count;azure_ifinerrors_maximum;azure_ifinerrors_minimum;azure_ifinerrors_total
Description: For packet-oriented interfaces, the number of inbound packets that contained errors preventing them from being deliverable to a higher-layer protocol.

Name: azure_ifinfcserrors_average;azure_ifinfcserrors_count;azure_ifinfcserrors_maximum;azure_ifinfcserrors_minimum;azure_ifinfcserrors_total
Description: Number of received packets which had errors in the frame check sequence (FCS), i.e., framing errors.

Name: azure_ifinmulticastpkts_average;azure_ifinmulticastpkts_count;azure_ifinmulticastpkts_maximum;azure_ifinmulticastpkts_minimum;azure_ifinmulticastpkts_total
Description: The number of packets, delivered by this sub-layer to a higher (sub-)layer, that were addressed to a multicast address at this sub-layer. For a MAC-layer protocol, this includes both Group and Functional addresses.

Name: azure_ifinoctets_average;azure_ifinoctets_count;azure_ifinoctets_maximum;azure_ifinoctets_minimum;azure_ifinoctets_total
Description: The total number of octets received on the interface, including framing characters.

Name: azure_ifinpkts_average;azure_ifinpkts_count;azure_ifinpkts_maximum;azure_ifinpkts_minimum;azure_ifinpkts_total
Description: The total number of packets received on the interface, including all unicast, multicast, broadcast and bad packets etc.

Name: azure_ifinunicastpkts_average;azure_ifinunicastpkts_count;azure_ifinunicastpkts_maximum;azure_ifinunicastpkts_minimum;azure_ifinunicastpkts_total
Description: The number of packets, delivered by this sub-layer to a higher (sub-)layer, that were not addressed to a multicast or broadcast address at this sub-layer.

Name: azure_ifoutbroadcastpkts_average;azure_ifoutbroadcastpkts_count;azure_ifoutbroadcastpkts_maximum;azure_ifoutbroadcastpkts_minimum;azure_ifoutbroadcastpkts_total
Description: The total number of packets that higher-level protocols requested be transmitted, and that were addressed to a broadcast address at this sub-layer, including those that were discarded or not sent.

Name: azure_ifoutdiscards_average;azure_ifoutdiscards_count;azure_ifoutdiscards_maximum;azure_ifoutdiscards_minimum;azure_ifoutdiscards_total
Description: The number of outbound packets that were chosen to be discarded even though no errors had been detected to prevent their being transmitted.

Name: azure_ifouterrors_average;azure_ifouterrors_count;azure_ifouterrors_maximum;azure_ifouterrors_minimum;azure_ifouterrors_total
Description: For packet-oriented interfaces, the number of outbound packets that could not be transmitted because of errors.

Name: azure_ifoutmulticastpkts_average;azure_ifoutmulticastpkts_count;azure_ifoutmulticastpkts_maximum;azure_ifoutmulticastpkts_minimum;azure_ifoutmulticastpkts_total
Description: The total number of packets that higher-level protocols requested be transmitted, and that were addressed to a multicast address at this sub-layer, including those that were discarded or not sent. For a MAC-layer protocol, this includes both Group and Functional addresses.

Name: azure_ifoutoctets_average;azure_ifoutoctets_count;azure_ifoutoctets_maximum;azure_ifoutoctets_minimum;azure_ifoutoctets_total
Description: The total number of octets transmitted out of the interface, including framing characters.

Name: azure_ifoutpkts_average;azure_ifoutpkts_count;azure_ifoutpkts_maximum;azure_ifoutpkts_minimum;azure_ifoutpkts_total
Description: The total number of packets transmitted out of the interface, including all unicast, multicast, broadcast, and bad packets etc.

Name: azure_ifoutunicastpkts_average;azure_ifoutunicastpkts_count;azure_ifoutunicastpkts_maximum;azure_ifoutunicastpkts_minimum;azure_ifoutunicastpkts_total
Description: The total number of packets that higher-level requested be transmitted, and that were not addressed to a multicast or broadcast address at this sub-layer, including those that were discarded or not sent.

Name: azure_interfaceoperstatus_average;azure_interfaceoperstatus_count;azure_interfaceoperstatus_maximum;azure_interfaceoperstatus_minimum;azure_interfaceoperstatus_total
Description: The current operational state of the interface. State is represented in numerical form. Up: 0, Down: 1, Lower_layer_down: 2, Testing: 3, Unknown: 4, Dormant: 5, Not_present: 6.

Name: azure_lacperrors_average;azure_lacperrors_count;azure_lacperrors_maximum;azure_lacperrors_minimum;azure_lacperrors_total

Name: azure_lacpinpkts_average;azure_lacpinpkts_count;azure_lacpinpkts_maximum;azure_lacpinpkts_minimum;azure_lacpinpkts_total
Description: Number of LACPDUs received.

Name: azure_lacpoutpkts_average;azure_lacpoutpkts_count;azure_lacpoutpkts_maximum;azure_lacpoutpkts_minimum;azure_lacpoutpkts_total
Description: Number of LACPDUs transmitted.

Name: azure_lacprxerrors_average;azure_lacprxerrors_count;azure_lacprxerrors_maximum;azure_lacprxerrors_minimum;azure_lacprxerrors_total
Description: Number of LACPDU receive packet errors.

Name: azure_lacptxerrors_average;azure_lacptxerrors_count;azure_lacptxerrors_maximum;azure_lacptxerrors_minimum;azure_lacptxerrors_total
Description: Number of LACPDU transmit packet errors.

Name: azure_lacpunknownerrors_average;azure_lacpunknownerrors_count;azure_lacpunknownerrors_maximum;azure_lacpunknownerrors_minimum;azure_lacpunknownerrors_total
Description: Number of LACPDU unknown packet errors.

Name: azure_lldpframein_average;azure_lldpframein_count;azure_lldpframein_maximum;azure_lldpframein_minimum;azure_lldpframein_total
Description: The number of lldp frames received.

Name: azure_lldpframeout_average;azure_lldpframeout_count;azure_lldpframeout_maximum;azure_lldpframeout_minimum;azure_lldpframeout_total
Description: The number of frames transmitted out.

Name: azure_lldptlvunknown_average;azure_lldptlvunknown_count;azure_lldptlvunknown_maximum;azure_lldptlvunknown_minimum;azure_lldptlvunknown_total
Description: The number of frames received with unknown TLV.

Name: azure_memoryavailable_average;azure_memoryavailable_count;azure_memoryavailable_maximum;azure_memoryavailable_minimum;azure_memoryavailable_total
Description: The available memory physically installed, or logically allocated to the component.

Name: azure_memoryutilized_average;azure_memoryutilized_count;azure_memoryutilized_maximum;azure_memoryutilized_minimum;azure_memoryutilized_total
Description: The memory currently in use by processes running on the component, not considering reserved memory that is not available for use.

Name: azure_powersupplycapacity_average;azure_powersupplycapacity_count;azure_powersupplycapacity_maximum;azure_powersupplycapacity_minimum;azure_powersupplycapacity_total
Description: Maximum power capacity of the power supply (watts).

Name: azure_powersupplyinputcurrent_average;azure_powersupplyinputcurrent_count;azure_powersupplyinputcurrent_maximum;azure_powersupplyinputcurrent_minimum;azure_powersupplyinputcurrent_total
Description: The input current draw of the power supply (amps).

Name: azure_powersupplyinputvoltage_average;azure_powersupplyinputvoltage_count;azure_powersupplyinputvoltage_maximum;azure_powersupplyinputvoltage_minimum;azure_powersupplyinputvoltage_total
Description: Input voltage to the power supply (volts).

Name: azure_powersupplyoutputcurrent_average;azure_powersupplyoutputcurrent_count;azure_powersupplyoutputcurrent_maximum;azure_powersupplyoutputcurrent_minimum;azure_powersupplyoutputcurrent_total
Description: The output current supplied by the power supply (amps)

Description: Output power supplied by the power supply (watts)

Name: azure_powersupplyoutputvoltage_average;azure_powersupplyoutputvoltage_count;azure_powersupplyoutputvoltage_maximum;azure_powersupplyoutputvoltage_minimum;azure_powersupplyoutputvoltage_total
Description: Output voltage supplied by the power supply (volts).

Name: azure_temperaturemax_average;azure_temperaturemax_count;azure_temperaturemax_maximum;azure_temperaturemax_minimum;azure_temperaturemax_total
Description: Max temperature in degrees Celsius of the component. The maximum value of the statistic over the sampling period.
